781
00:36:40,260 --> 00:36:41,539
He'll believe it fell out.

782
00:36:41,539 --> 00:36:44,500
All right, on three, we just all jump off, okay?

783
00:36:44,500 --> 00:36:48,180
Three, two, one, okay, dexterity savings right now.

784
